---

<section id="empresa" class="about-section source-container reveal">
  <div class="about-layout">
    <aside class="about-aside">
      <h3>
        Somos una empresa de software enfocada en pequeñas y medianas empresas.
      </h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Oaxaca, México</li>
        <li>Atención local y remota</li>
        <li>Sistemas a medida</li>
        <li>Automatización de procesos</li>
        <li>Soporte continuo</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>

    <div class="about-content">
      <span class="about-kicker">Empresa de desarrollo de software</span>

      <h2>
        ADNOVA Software Solutions crea soluciones digitales para empresas que quieren ordenar procesos, reducir tareas manuales y tomar mejores decisiones.
      </h2>

      <p class="about-typewriter">
        <span>Diseñamos sistemas digitales para operar con más control.</span>
      </p>

      <a href="/nosotros" class="about-button">
        Sobre nosotros
        <span>↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.3fr 0.7fr;
    gap: 88px;
    padding: 86px 54px 96px;
  }

  .about-aside {
    display: grid;
    align-content: start;
    gap: 38px;
  }

  .about-aside h3 {
    max-width: 330px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: clamp(21px, 1.8vw, 30px);
    line-height: 1.12;
    font-weight: var(--weight-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.052em;
  }

  .about-aside ul {
    display: grid;
    gap: 13px;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-aside li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.18vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.32;
    font-weight: var(--weight-body);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .about-aside li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55em;
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    align-content: start;
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .about-kicker {
    width: fit-content;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--weight-strong);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-kicker::before {
    content: "";
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: clamp(34px, 3.8vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1.04;
    font-weight: var(--weight-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.065em;
  }

  .about-typewriter {
    width: fit-content;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 1.35vw, 23px);
    line-height: 1.35;
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
  }

  .about-typewriter span {
    display: inline-block;
    max-width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-right: 2px solid var(--blue);
    animation:
      typing 3.2s steps(58, end) both,
      caret 0.85s step-end infinite;
  }

  .about-button {
    width: min(360px, 100%);
    min-height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding: 0 24px;
    background: var(--black);
    color: white;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      background 0.25s ease,
      transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  .about-button:hover {
    background: var(--blue);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .about-button span {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @keyframes typing {
    from {
      width: 0;
    }

    to {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @keyframes caret {
    50% {
      border-color: transparent;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 54px;
      padding: 74px 34px 84px;
    }

    .about-aside {
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    .about-aside h3 {
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .about-aside ul {
      max-width: 680px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 13px 28px;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      max-width: 920px;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5.7vw, 58px);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .about-section {
      border-left: 0;
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .about-layout {
      display: block;
      padding: 64px 20px 72px;
    }

    .about-aside {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .about-aside h3 {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
      font-size: clamp(24px, 6.4vw, 34px);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.052em;
    }

    .about-aside ul {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 11px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .about-aside li {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .about-content {
      gap: 26px;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      max-width: 100%;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 8.6vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.06;
      letter-spacing: -0.058em;
    }

    .about-typewriter {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .about-typewriter span {
      white-space: normal;
      border-right: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
    }

    .about-button {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 62px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .about-layout {
      padding-top: 56px;
      padding-bottom: 64px;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 8vw, 40px);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about-typewriter span {
      width: auto;
      border-right: 0;
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(14px);
    }

    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
